# 资产目录与模板同处 data/。默认忽略个人卡和游玩产物，
# 仅跟踪目录占位符与带 .template.yml 后缀的模板卡。
*
!.gitignore
!characters/
!characters/.gitkeep
!characters/*.template.yml
!entities/
!entities/.gitkeep
!entities/*.template.yml
!styles/
!styles/.gitkeep
!styles/*.template.yml
!worldbooks/
!worldbooks/.gitkeep
!worldbooks/*.template.yml
!saves/
!saves/.gitkeep
